| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-3054 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 42fd3c0a-a466-51e0-abfa-d1bc9dc84038"
